					<div class="commentheading">On December 26, 2005 at 11:14 PM, Paul Y (guest) said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Clam Chowder On Fridays</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">Clam Chowder and Fish are generally served on Fridays due to the teachings of the church regarding the bible.<br />
<br />
